com.interpss.dc.pv.inverter

Interface DcAcInverter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AbstractDcAcInverter, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IDcAcInverter, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DcAcInverterImpl

    public interface DcAcInverter
extends AbstractDcAcInverter
    A representation of the model object 'Dc Ac Inverter'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Power Rating W
    • Rated Vac
    • PFactor
    • Vdcmax
    • Idcmax
    • Mppt High
    • Mppt Low
    • Loss Data Type
    • Loss Eqn
    • Loss Eqn Param Table
    See Also:
    DcAcInverterPackage.getDcAcInverter()
